data.description: ESSENTIAL FLORIDA LIVING awaits at this stunning, waterfront property, situated within the coveted Tiger Point community. Enter through the custom front doors (w/ iron details) and step into the foyer, where you’ll be greeted by soaring ceilings, travertine floors, and views to your waterfront rear yard. The great room features a grand, wood-burning fireplace, hardwood floors, and custom stair rail to the second floor. The formal dining room connects to the gourmet kitchen. Unleash your culinary artistry within this space, including: center island with 5-burner gas cooktop, commercial hood vent, wine cooler, black-cherry cabinets, wall oven/built-in microwave, and granite counters. All bedrooms are designed to have an en-suite bath, with both an upstairs and downstairs master. The spacious, lower-level suite has water views, a walk-in closet, and luxurious bathroom with glass shower, jetted tub, and double vanity with vessel sinks. Completing the first floor is the screened-porch with plenty of room for gathering/entertaining with family and friends. Your backyard outdoor oasis has a pond, tropical plants, open deck, and dock for fishing or feeding the turtles at the water’s edge! Upstairs are 3 additional bedrooms. 2 share a full bath and the 2nd master bedroom has a private bath. In addition, the home has a new roof (2021), 2 new HVAC units (2022), all new carpeting, and newer water heater (2020). Tiger Point is a golf cart-friendly neighborhood that is home to The Pointe Restaurant, club house, a semi-private golf course, recreation areas, walking paths, and entrance to Soundside Nature Preserve. Gulf Breeze is one of the Gulf Coast’s most sought-after locations, due to the A-rated schools, excellent dining and shopping options, and quick access to: airport, Downtown, Milton, Navarre, and the sugar white sands of Pensacola Beach. This must-see, coastal country-club home is Florida at its finest!
